Colombia Bond Rating Boosted to Investment Grade by Moody’s; Peso Advances

-- B y   B i l l   K o e n i g
-- 
2011-05-31T16:43:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/colombia-bond-rating-boosted-to-investment-grade-by-moody-s-peso-advances.html
Moody’s Investors Service said it
upgraded the Colombian government’s foreign-currency bond rating
to Baa3, or investment grade, from Ba1.  The outlook is stable, Moody’s said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bill Koenig at 
